Description: Snake Ventures Game
 A modern implementation of the classic Snake game with multiple difficulty levels,
 dynamic themes, and resizable window support. Features include:
 * Three difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, and Hard
 * Dynamic color themes for each difficulty
 * Resizable game window
 * Pause functionality
 * Score tracking
